%p Hello #{@email},

- if @resource.try(:unconfirmed_email?)
  %p
    We're contacting you to notify you that your email is being changed to
    = succeed '.' do
      %strong= @resource.unconfirmed_email
- else
  %p
    We're contacting you to notify you that your email has been changed to
    = succeed '.' do
      %strong= @resource.email

%p{ style: 'margin-top: 24px;' } If you did not make this change, please contact us immediately.

%p
  Best regards,
  %br
  The Corsego Team

%p{ style: 'font-size: 12px; color: #6c757d;' }= link_to 'Visit Corsego', root_url
